Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:01:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my Lost Memory World...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back in Egypt three thousand years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle between Bakura and me has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stealing and killing... and showing no respect for the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura, I cannot forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Bakura got away and his whereabouts was unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado brought a group of guards with him and headed to the tomb, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle to the Death!\N Mahado VS Bakura"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, the entrance is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the thief can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the stone tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a {\i1}Ka{\i0} should appear on this tablet, we have been ordered to seal this tomb forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Mahado is prepared to give up his life for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to allow him to fight in peace, we must prevent all possible interferences!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at the risk of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really{\i0} now? I'm happy to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dying to give that Millennium Ring to me {\i1}that badly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hand the Millennium Ring over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will not walk out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are pretty bold words coming from such a lowly spellcaster as yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will unleash the entirety of my magical energies, my {\i1}Heka{\i0}, for this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For generations, magicians have trained their magical powers in this training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura! Today, this place will become your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The appearance of his {\i1}Ka{\i0}.. his Diabound has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time my hatred grows,\N Diabound evolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll release {\i1}all{\i0} of my repressed {\i1}Heka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon forth Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your {\i1}Ka{\i0} has become more powerful than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're no match for my Diabound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me put that to the test, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diaha!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Poison Fangs Strike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In just a flash, he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Blast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I give my {\i1}Heka{\i0}\N to Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Magic Blasts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy... is no ordinary magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura... Even if it costs me all the {\i0}Heka{\i1} I have within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this feeling of uneasiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Mahado's Shrine of {\i1}Wedju{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no wind but the light is flickering...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your {\i1}Ba{\i0} should be reduced as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just right for a {\i1}warm up{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound's finally gotten {\i1}heated up{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Then I shall give you more "warmth"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much so that your very {\i1}mind and soul{\i0} will burn in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound, counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wall Concealed {\i1}Ka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a new {\i1}Ka{\i0} hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Special Power of Shadow Ghoul, Wall Concealment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Blast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Ghoul! Consecutive Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear the enemy to shreds! Shadow Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that the same trick would work twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Ghoul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magus of Illusion...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Blast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound, kill the Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend... Why are you able to use Shadow Ghoul's Wall Concealment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! Oh yeah, I never mentioned this earlier, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound's Special Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It steals the Special Powers of the {\i1}Ka{\i0} it defeats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a special ability fitting for a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let me get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Mahado specifically ordered us that no one is to enter before he returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we abide by Pharaoh's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come to Mahado's Shrine of {\i1}Wedju?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I saw Master in great pain within my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be overreacting, but I got so worried I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I came here, I might be able to sense what Master's feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Mahado in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tablet is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... \NMahado summoned his {\i1}Ka?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magus of Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been marking the doors with a magic marker so we know which paths we've tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marking your territory, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just something Jounouchi'd do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In another sense, you're just tagging someone's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already went this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, we're going in {\i1}circles{\i0} around the same path!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Can't you hear us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're calling you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is the right door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you don't care what happens to Yugi if we can't get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart hurts when I go near this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's up with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It vanished along with the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the true enemy the Pharaoh will have to fight against.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self's true enemy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician scum!\N That's about all you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The likes of yourself never had a chance of winning against someone as great as {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly rank in that level!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then... Guess I should finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That trap is a {\i1}real{\i0} trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has always been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply casting a spell so you couldn't {\i1}see{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using such cheap tricks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura! I'll resort to any means necessary if it means defeating you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was {\i1}close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to perish by the very trap you set {\i1}yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what I was after!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound! Smash that magician and his {\i1}Ka{\i0} until nothing remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado... Don't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could... Mahado be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in the Valley of the Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the training hall for spellcasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight, Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mahado?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's inside the training hall... with Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, inform everyone at the royal palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these things immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! I'll take you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this match is mine, Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking your Millennium Ring now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Great Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really wanted to see the new world you've wanted to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I can assist in fulfilling that wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'm very willing to sacrifice my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've warned him so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... still wants to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not have much {\i1}Heka{\i0} remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you... the forbidden ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forbidden ritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give my life as sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to fuse my spirit and my soul,\N my {\i1}Ba{\i0} and {\i1}Ka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't let this bother you-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prince, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One who will become the Pharaoh doing such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what is the difference between me and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is your eternal servant!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he killed {\i1}himself{\i0} in the end, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's his {\i1}Ka{\i0} still here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did he really fuse his {\i1}Ba{\i0} and {\i1}Ka{\i0} together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the peace of the people, and for the new ideal world that the Pharaoh hopes for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound, finish off this half-dead fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Blast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado... How can this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Labyrinth is... trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado... sacrificed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh... My soul is\N your eternal servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self's heart is trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, this maze is his heart, one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart is being swallowed by loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only ones who can hear his loneliness and his sad cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's no use in us continuing to check all the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's the other me who's knocking at the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we must concentrate and listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, we must listen carefully for the cries of the other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado sacrificed himself in order to carry out the forbidden ritual...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Bakura disappeared\N from sight once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this really the end of the duel with and Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, we found the True Door...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And managed to come into Yugi's Lost Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is it that nobody here notices us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Blue-Eyed Kisara"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
